data.description: MOTIVATED SELLERS!! ** NEW ** NEW ** NEW 30 YEAR ARCHITECTURAL ROOF & NEW PAINT THROUGHOUT THE HOME* Come check out this like new home at 29 EMERALD DRIVE today and see what 3,329 SQUARE FEET provides you with in the desirable PIKE ROAD area!!! Located conveniently near Publix, Walmart, Target, and the Shoppes at Eastchase you will find it easy to get to all the LOCAL AMENITIES of Pike Road and Montgomery! This Property boasts AMPLE AMOUNTS OF ROOM! With FIVE BEDROOMS and TWO BONUS ROOMS that could serve as two additional bedrooms or even a game room or movie room, making 29 Emerald Drive perfect for someone seeking a home with an EXTENSIVE amounts of space! Find yourself ENTERTAINING in the large open EAT-IN KITCHEN and living room that opens up to the backyard. Come home after a long day to relax in your OVERSIZED Master Bedroom with room enough for a sitting room, and enjoy soaking in the LARGE GARDEN TUB or take a hop into the Large Tiled Shower!!! The Master Suite also has two LARGE WALK-IN CLOSETS located off the Master Bathroom with room enough for those who appreciate clothes, shoes, bags, etc. 29 Emerald Drive is within WALKING DISTANCE of the amenities that the Stone Park neighborhood includes; such as the SWIMMING POOL, and onsite PLAYGROUND!  Schedule your own private tour today at 29 Emerald Drive and make Stone Park your new home!
